    <entry>
      <title>Hexo音乐视频播放插件-非平台API</title>
      <link href="2021/01/25/Video&amp;Music/"/>
      <url>2021/01/25/Video&amp;Music/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="Dplayer介绍"><a href="#Dplayer介绍" class="headerlink" title="Dplayer介绍"></a>Dplayer介绍</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-dplayer">hexo-tag-dplayer</a> 是 <a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/DPlayer">APlayer</a> 播放器的 Hexo 标签插件，可以十分方便地在文章内插入视频播放器。</p><h4 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><p>hexo根目录执行：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-tag-dplayer --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改 Hexo 的站点配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code> ，增加</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo-tag-dplayer:</span><br><span class="line">  cdn:</span><br><span class="line">    - https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;dplayer&#x2F;dist&#x2F;DPlayer.min.js</span><br><span class="line">    - https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;dplayer&#x2F;dist&#x2F;DPlayer.min.css</span><br><span class="line">  default: </span><br><span class="line">    api: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;api.prprpr.me&#x2F;dplayer&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">    loop: yes</span><br><span class="line">    screenshot: yes</span><br><span class="line">    # 后面还可以接着写其他默认配置</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h4><p>使用 hexo-tag-dplayer 非常简单，只需要在 MarkDown 文件中插入正确的标记就可以了。</p><h5 id="Markdown"><a href="#Markdown" class="headerlink" title="Markdown"></a>Markdown</h5><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% dplayer &quot;url&#x3D;视频地址&quot; %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h4><div id="dplayer0" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer0"),"loop":"yes","screenshot":"yes","video":{"url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/HonestLiu/Gallery@master/%E8%99%B9.mp4"},"danmaku":{"api":"https://api.prprpr.me/dplayer/"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script><h2 id="Aplayer"><a href="#Aplayer" class="headerlink" title="Aplayer"></a>Aplayer</h2><h4 id="安装-1"><a href="#安装-1" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><p>hexo根目录执行：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-tag-aplayer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="使用-1"><a href="#使用-1" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% aplayer &quot;歌曲名&quot; &quot;作者&quot; &quot;歌曲url&quot; &quot;封面url&quot; &quot;autoplay&quot; %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="示例-1"><a href="#示例-1" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h4>        <div id="aplayer-jsBcddMs" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">            <pre class="aplayer-lrc-content"></pre>        </div>        <script>          var ap = new APlayer({            element: document.getElementById("aplayer-jsBcddMs"),            narrow: false,            autoplay: false,            showlrc: false,            music: {              title: "万有引力",              author: "F*yy",              url: "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/HonestLiu/Gallery@master/%E4%B8%87%E6%9C%89%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B-Fyy.mp3",              pic: "https://p1.music.126.net/PzVklWfH2G1gVuHd3a50Gg==/109951164984873532.jpg",              lrc: ""            }          });          window.aplayers || (window.aplayers = []);          window.aplayers.push(ap);        </script>]]></content>
      
      
      
